- `vendor/axiom/` — Official AXIOM source (cloned from GitHub, installed editable)
- `vendor/gameworld/` — Official Gameworld environment suite
- `experiments/` — Sweep runner, config YAMLs defining parameter grids per phase
- `analysis/` — Plotting utilities, helpers, Jupyter notebooks for each phase
